                    <section class="content projetotemplate">
        <h1>FUTEBOL: Federated Union of Telecommunications Research Facilities for an EU-Brasil Open Laboratory</h1>
        <p><b>Description</b> This is a recently approved Horizon 2020 / BR-UE project, where UFES LabTel / NERDS participates in this pool of Institutions to provide and conduct scientific experiments on heterogeneous, wired and wireless communication networks. Under the leadership of UFRGS and Trinity College, the project also counts Unicamp, UFMG, UFC, Intel-Brasil and Digitel; Europe, Bristol, VTT (Finland), IT / PT (Portugal) and Intel (Germany).</p>
                <br /><br />
